LibrarySystem.Book

  • Uses of Book in LibrarySystem

    Methods in LibrarySystem with parameters of type Book
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void Library.add​(Book book)
    The add method adds a Book object to the bag data structure, when the bag is full, it calls the grow method to increases the size of the bag.
    boolean Library.checkOut​(Book book)
    The checkOut method calls the find method.
    boolean Library.remove​(Book book)
    The remove method removes a Book object from the bag data structure.
    boolean Library.returns​(Book book)
    The returns method calls the find method.
